ðŸ§  AI Object Detection System (YOLOv8 + FastAPI + Streamlit)

Real-time object detection system built using YOLOv9, integrated with FastAPI, Streamlit, and OpenCV, supporting image detection, video detection, webcam inference, and a desktop video viewer.

